<p>è¿›è¡Œå®Œ rebase åï¼Œç›´æ¥æ‰§è¡Œ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">git push origin your-branch-name</code> ä¼šå¤±è´¥ï¼Œè¿™æ—¶åƒä¸‡ä¸è¦æŒ‰ç…§æç¤ºè¿›è¡Œ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">git pull</code>ï¼Œå¦åˆ™ä¼šè§¦å‘ mergeã€‚</p>

